org.javimmutable.collections

Interface JImmutableSet<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cursorable<T>, Insertable<T,JImmutableSet<T>>, InvariantCheckable, Iterable<T>, IterableStreamable<T>, Mapped<T,T>, SplitableIterable<T>, Streamable<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JImmutableMultiset<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJImmutableMultiset, AbstractJImmutableSet, JImmutableHashMultiset, JImmutableHashSet, JImmutableInsertOrderMultiset, JImmutableInsertOrderSet, JImmutableTreeMultiset, JImmutableTreeSet

    @Immutable
public interface JImmutableSet<T>
extends Insertable<T,JImmutableSet<T>>, Cursorable<T>, IterableStreamable<T>, Mapped<T,T>, InvariantCheckable
    Interface for immutable sets.
